detectors.description:
Reentrancy in WarpVault.repay(uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#94-99):
	External calls:
	- IERC20(stablecoin).transferFrom(msg.sender,address(this),amount) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#97)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- positions[msg.sender].borrowed -= amount (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#98)
	WarpVault.positions (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#31) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- WarpVault.borrow(uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#53-66)
	- WarpVault.deposit(uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#45-48)
	- WarpVault.positions (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#31)
	- WarpVault.repay(uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#94-99)
	- WarpVault.withdraw(uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_017.sol#104-122)
